<title>100万人投他当总统，数万人因他戒毒…他是这届世界杯最开挂的人</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/ftKG3RtGA7</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/ftKG3RtGA7</guid>
